title: Air Hockey Glow Edition v1.1

Air Hockey Glow Edition: this is not just another game of its genre - a new game with new features:

Today, you try new gameplay elements, you forget about the other games of this genre, because the time to get bored you will not!
Call friends and start fighting on the field dvoem or four of them on the screen of one device!

4 game modes
Game one with support for up to 4 players
Game on bluetooth
Setting up points in all game modes
colorful design
nice music
